	<div class="container">
<h1><%= @events_locs %> </h1>
			<div class="section-box">
				<div class="navbar">
					<h2 class="welcome-banner">
					 Hi and Welcome to the 100 Motels demo site!<br>
					 <small>100 Motels is an idea I have to help independent musicians like myself get out on tour without industry backing or paying to play.</small>
					</h2>
	  			<div id="welcome-nav" class="navbar-inner" align="center">
	  				<div class="label-box">What do you want to do?</div>
						<ul class="nav">
							<li class="span2">
		    				<a href="#new-promoters">Tour or Support</a>
		  				</li>
		  				<li class="span3"><a href="#promoter-apply">Organize a show</a></li>
		  				<li class="span2"><a href="#latest-events">Buy a ticket</a></li>
		  				<li class="span3"><%= link_to "More about 100 Motels", info_path %></li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		<div id="content">
			<section id="latest-events">
				<header class="page-header">
					<h3>
						<i class="icon-globe"></i>
						Shows near <%= @location %>
					</h3>
				</header>
				<div id="events-carousel" class="carousel slide" data-interval="false">
					<div class="carousel-inner">
						<% @locations.each_slice(3) do |loc| %>
						<div class="item">
								<ul class="thumbnails">
									<li class="span4">
										<div class="thumbnail">
											<% if loc[0].event.image? %>
												<%= filepicker_image_tag loc[0].event.image, w: 360, h: 240, fit: 'crop' %>
											<% else %>
												<img src="http://quickimage.it/360x240&text=ArtistPic" alt="">
											<% end %>
											<div class="caption">
												<h4 class="title">
													<%= loc[0].event.artist %>
												</h4>
												<p><%= loc[0].event.venue %> on <%= time_tag loc[0].event.date %></p>
												<%= button_to "Info & Tickets", event_path(loc[0].event), method: :get, class: "btn btn-success", id: loc[0].event.artist %>
											</div>
										</div>
									</li>
									<li class="span4">
										<% if loc[1] %>
											<div class="thumbnail">
											<% if loc[1].event.image? %>
												<%= filepicker_image_tag loc[1].event.image, w: 360, h: 240, fit: 'crop' %>
											<% else %>
												<img src="http://quickimage.it/360x240&text=ArtistPic" alt="">
											<% end %>
											<div class="caption">
												<h4 class="title">
													<%= loc[1].event.artist %>
												</h4>
												<p><%= loc[1].event.venue %> on <%= time_tag loc[1].event.date %></p>
												<%= button_to "Info & Tickets", event_path(loc[1].event), method: :get, class: "btn btn-success", id: loc[1].event.artist %>
											</div>
											</div>
										<% else %>

										<% end %>
									</li>
									<li class="span4">
										<% if loc[2] %>
											<div class="thumbnail">
												<% if loc[2].event.image? %>
													<%= filepicker_image_tag loc[2].event.image, w: 360, h: 240, fit: 'crop' %>
												<% else %>
													<img src="http://quickimage.it/360x240&text=ArtistPic" alt="">
												<% end %>
												<div class="caption">
													<h4 class="title">
														<%= loc[2].event.artist %>
													</h4>
													<p><%= loc[2].event.venue %> on <%= time_tag loc[2].event.date %></p>
													<%= button_to "Info & Tickets", event_path(loc[2].event), method: :get, class: "btn btn-success", id: loc[2].event.artist %>
												</div>
											</div>
										<% else %>

										<% end %>
									</li>
								</ul>
						</div>
						<% end %>
					</div>
					<a class="left carousel-control" href="#events-carousel" data-slide="prev">‹</a>
					<a class="right carousel-control" href="#events-carousel" data-slide="next">›</a>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="new-promoters">
				<header>
					<h3 class="page-header"><i class="icon-globe"></i>Promoters near <%= @location %></h3>
				</header>
				<div id="promoters-carousel" class="carousel slide" data-interval="false">
					<div id="promoters" class="carousel-inner">
						<% @profiles.each_slice(4) do |profile| %>
						<div class="item">
								<ul class="thumbnails">
									<li class="span3">
										<div class="thumbnail">
											<% if profile[0] %>
												<% if profile[0].image? %>
				                  <%= filepicker_image_tag profile[0].image, w: 360, h: 360, fit: 'crop' %>
				                <% else %>
				                  <img src="http://placehold.it/360x360" alt="">
				                <% end %>
													<div class="caption">
														<h3 class="title"><%= profile[0].promoter_name || profile[0].user.name %></h3>
														<h4>location</h4>
														<%= button_to "Full Profile", promoter_profile_path(profile[0]), method: :get, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
												</div>
											<% end %>
										</div>
									</li>
									<li class="span3">
										<div class="thumbnail">
											<% if profile[1] %>
												<% if profile[1].image? %>
				                  <%= filepicker_image_tag profile[1].image, w: 360, h: 360, fit: 'crop' %>
				                <% else %>
				                  <img src="http://placehold.it/360x360" alt="">
				                <% end %>
												<div class="caption">
													<h3 class="title"><%= profile[1].promoter_name || profile[1].user.name %></h3>
													<h4>location</h4>
													<%= button_to "Full Profile", promoter_profile_path(profile[1]), method: :get, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
												</div>
											<% end %>
										</div>
									</li>
									<li class="span3">
										<div class="thumbnail">
											<% if profile[2] %>
												<% if profile[2].image? %>
				                  <%= filepicker_image_tag profile[2].image, w: 360, h: 360, fit: 'crop' %>
				                <% else %>
				                  <img src="http://placehold.it/360x360" alt="">
				                <% end %>
												<div class="caption">
													<h3 class="title"><%= profile[2].promoter_name || profile[2].user.name %></h3>
													<h4>location</h4>
													<%= button_to "Full Profile", promoter_profile_path(profile[2]), method: :get, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
												</div>
											<% end %>
										</div>
									</li>
									<li class="span3">
										<div class="thumbnail">
											<% if profile[3] %>
												<% if profile[3].image? %>
				                  <%= filepicker_image_tag profile[3].image, w: 360, h: 360, fit: 'crop' %>
				                <% else %>
				                  <img src="http://placehold.it/360x360" alt="">
				                <% end %>
												<div class="caption">
													<h3 class="title"><%= profile[3].promoter_name || profile[3].user.name %></h3>
													<h4>location</h4>
													<%= button_to "Full Profile", promoter_profile_path(profile[3]), method: :get, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
												</div>
											<% end %>
										</div>
									</li>
								</ul>
						</div>
						<% end %>
					</div>
					<a class="left carousel-control" href="#promoters-carousel" data-slide="prev">‹</a>
					<a class="right carousel-control" href="#promoters-carousel" data-slide="next">›</a>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="promoter-apply">
				<div class="well well-large">
					<h3>Looking to put on Shows?...Apply to become a Member</h3>
					<blockquote>
						<p> Initially at least my idea is to vet prospective promoters as opposed to having a completely open community, although there is technically no reason to prevent the latter. There could be a fee for membership dependent on the level of promoter activity.</p><br>
						<p>Ordinary users can choose to create an account with 100 Motels when purchasing tickets but for promoters there's a different process. </p>
					<p>If you click the signup button below you will be taken to Stripe.com to either authorize an existing account for use with 100 Motels or to create one.
						This enables promoters to be paid directly and is only available to US or Canadian citizens at the time of writing.</p>
						<p>100 Motels recieves a per transaction fee for each ticket purchased while Stripe's processing fees are applied directly to the promoter's account.</p> <br>
						<p>For more details on this and all other technical queries regarding the service click on the 'More Info' button below.</p>
					</blockquote>
					<div class="btn-group">
						<a href="#invite" class="btn btn-large btn-primary" data-toggle="modal">Request Invite</a>
					  <%= link_to "More Info", info_path, class: "btn btn-large" %>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
		<div class="modal hide fade" id="invite" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">x</button>
        <h3>100 Motels Promoter Invites</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>Thanks for your interest. Right now I'm testing amongst people I know, so if you've stumbled onto this site somehow this is really only a demo, 100 Motels is not open for business yet. If you want to contact me about getting involved message me on twitter, facebook, github or whatever you use, <a href="//seocahill.com">Seo.</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <a href="#" class="btn" data-dismiss="modal">Close</a>
      </div>
    </div>
	</div>




